title.rendered: Reynard Prep Pads 70% Isopropyl Alcohol 6cm x 6cm Prep Pads, 200 Pack

content.rendered:
Reynard’s Sterile alcohol prep pads are much larger than most prep pad and contain high levels of moisture for the purpose of covering larger areas offering more effective cleansing.

 

Ideal for use in

·         Hospitals

·         Palliative Care Facilities

·         Doctors Surgeries

·         Dental Practices

·         Pathology Laboratories

·         Tattoo parlours

·         Cosmetic Surgeries

·         Aged Care
